name: Art@Altitude
overview:
100% New Zealand handmade. We offer beautifully crafted and finished New Zealand Art and Crafts at huge discounted wholesale prices. Whether it is for landscaping ideas or simply to add a piece of eligance to your home and garden we are definately the most affordable for both retailers and home owners alike. Very popular art both overseas in here in New Zealand, as both exclusive garden decor or simple home decor. We offer massive wholesale discounts for retailers and bulk orders worldwide from 15% to 50% off RRP.

All of Art@Altitudes Indoor / Outdoor Wall Art, Garden Art, Wall Hangings, Sculptures , Home Decor and Pavers are made from aggregate Sand/cement and can be beautifully handpainted to any colours of your choosing or acid washed to expose the raw sand or aggregate.

We sell ABS Plastics Moulds / Molds of just about all our handmade products. We use 1.5mm durable commercial grade ABS plastic that will last for 100’s of pours if not more…For use with concrete, plaster or clay…easy to use…easy to clean…. Moulds 4 you by Art@Altitude We also sell ABS plastic moulds4you STARTER KITS. These contain everything you will need to prepare, pour, finish, seal, paint and sell your product. It has been a very popular item not only as a starter kit for the absolute novice but also as a wonderful gift for friend or family. Moulds4you by Art@Altitude

You can easily purchase our pre-made kits or design your own kit to suit. All members will be entitled to a 15% discount when purchasing from our products store
